# Pre-publish additions (2026-05-28)
# Build/process artifacts that don't belong in a public repo:
#   - docs/superpowers/ holds the brainstormed spec + plans + validator
#     reports. Kept locally for reproducibility, not for redistribution.
#   - swa-docs/secrets-manager-saas-api*.yaml is CyberArk's public API
#     spec (downloaded from api-docs.cyberark.com) — referenceable, not
#     redistributable.
#   - Any PDFs that may sneak in (PANW brand guidelines, datasheets, etc.)
#     are gitignored as a class.
docs/superpowers/
swa-docs/secrets-manager-saas-api*.yaml
*.pdf
